description:
EA Sports brings back the best football simulation in another installment of the renowned FIFA series. FIFA 22 uses groundbreaking technology to deliver the most realistic simulation and the best football experience to all players, especially on next-gen consoles. The game takes data imported from the real world to deliver true ball physics and includes a brand new Explosive Sprint mechanic that will give players more control of their speed when dribbling or defending. The goalkeepers have been reworked in FIFA 22, and now they are far smarter, with improved decision-making and positioning between the posts. The new Hyper Motion system takes advantage of the next-gen consoles' capabilities to create an experience that feels more organic than ever for maximum realism.

FIFA 22 features plenty of gameplay modes, including the return of Volta Football, a Career Mode that will allow you to create a club and guide it to the top, and a revamped Player Career experience with more options to develop your star player than ever. Of course, FUT is back in FIFA 22 too. You will be able to put your skill to the test against other players with a new seasonal progression, Elite Division matches, co-op public matchmaking and expanded customization options for your stadiums.  Also, FUT Heroes will bring back some of the most iconic football players of all time.

FIFA 22 is the game that all football fans deserve. With licensed teams from the most important leagues from all over the world, it offers the ultimate football simulation experience.
